' Measure distance with Ping))) sensor and display in centimeters.
' {$STAMP BS2}
' {$PBASIC 2.5}
' Conversion constants for room temperature measurements.
CmConstant CON 2260 ' room temp
'CmConstant CON 2169 ' 0 degrees
cmDistance VAR Word
time VAR Word

DO
  PULSOUT 15, 5
  PULSIN 15, 1, time

  cmDistance = CmConstant ** time
  DEBUG HOME, DEC3 cmDistance, " cm"
  PAUSE 100
LOOP

' Temperatur error between 0 C and 22 C would be 3.9%
' Distance error at 1m would be 3.9cm short